@baseUrl = http://localhost:5140/api/menus

### List all menus (from PG view)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### List menus by owner
GET {{baseUrl}}?ownerId=rest-001

### Get a single menu
# Replace {menuId} with a real menu ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{menuId}

### Update a menu
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{menuId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Lunch Special",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "isActive": true
}

### Get menu stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/{menuId}/stats

### Soft-delete a menu
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{menuId}
